item.title: About
item.description: Result-driven professional with experience in academic research looking to transition into software engineering. His previous role required strong time management skills and high communication skills. Furthermore, having followed good coding practices in every project he has been involved, he is expected to quickly adapt to a software role. A highly motivated individual eager to proving himself in a new role. GitHub Linkedin CV
